reviewText: I received this item in a timely fashion. This dvd will not play on my dvd players, one is a blue ray player, the other is not. I also tried to play it on my laptop and was unable as well. I really wanted to see this video, but I can't. Disappointed.

Fishing from the British point of view.  I was disappointed that the disc was not region 1 like the description said. Had to watch on computer.  Video was a nice change of pace from  american fishing shows. I would watch more.
